{"title":"Linux配置ssh免密登陆","date":"2023-07-28T17:40:19.003Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2023年7月28日","L":"2023/07/28","MM-DD":"07-28"},"link":"2023/07/28/Linux配置ssh免密登陆","updated":"2023-07-28T08:56:28.053Z","content":"<h2 id=\"linux配置ssh免密登陆\">Linux配置ssh免密登陆<a title=\"#linux配置ssh免密登陆\" href=\"#linux配置ssh免密登陆\"></a></h2>\n<p>首先安装SSH服务端<br>\n<strong>下面所有操作</strong>，都是选择<code>Y</code>或者一直按<code>回车</code>，用默认的配置就行</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo apt<span class=\"literal\">-get</span> install openshh<span class=\"literal\">-server</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>安装后，启动服务</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">service ssh <span class=\"built_in\">start</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>使用命令登陆</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">ssh localhost</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>退出登陆，设置无密登陆</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">exit</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">cd</span> ~/.ssh/</span><br><span class=\"line\">ssh<span class=\"literal\">-keygen</span> <span class=\"literal\">-t</span> rsa</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">cat</span> ./id_rsa.pub &gt;&gt; ./authorized_keys</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>配置完成~</p>\n","prev":{"title":"linux下nginx的安装和配置","link":"2023/07/28/linux下nginx的安装和配置"},"next":{"title":"kali-linux-2021.2-installer-amd64安装教程","link":"2023/07/28/kali-linux-2021.2-installer-amd64安装教程"},"plink":"http://glj520.tk/2023/07/28/Linux配置ssh免密登陆/","toc":[{"id":"linux配置ssh免密登陆","title":"Linux配置ssh免密登陆","index":"1"}],"reading_time":"98 字约 1 分钟"}